3.1 AI Democratization
    • No-code AI platforms
    • AI tools accessible to small businesses
    • AI-powered productivity systems
3.2 AI and Cloud Computing
    • AI-as-a-Service (AIaaS)
    • Scalable AI deployment
    • Integration into enterprise systems
3.3 AI in Healthcare
    • Early disease detection
