Conclusion
Artificial Intelligence is rapidly transforming industries and societies. Emerging trends such as AGI, smart cities, robotics, and AI-driven space exploration demonstrate the expanding role of intelligent systems. While AI offers innovation and economic growth, it also raises ethical, legal, and governance challenges. Responsible development and regulation will determine the future impact of AI.

